description: Return a list of operations that occurred on an App Runner service. The resulting list of  OperationSummary objects is sorted in reverse chronological order. The first object on the list represents the last started operation.

parameters.name: ServiceArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the App Runner service that you want a list of operations for.

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description: A token from a previous result page. It's used for a paginated request. The request retrieves the next result page. All other parameter values must be identical to the ones specified in the initial request. If you don't specify NextToken, the request retrieves the first result page.

parameters.name: MaxResults
parameters.description: The maximum number of results to include in each response (result page). It's used for a paginated request. If you don't specify MaxResults, the request retrieves all available results in a single response.

nested_items.name: OperationSummaryList
nested_items.description: A list of operation summary information records. In a paginated request, the request returns up to MaxResults records for each call.

nested_items.name: Id
nested_items.description: A unique ID of this operation. It's unique in the scope of the App Runner service.

nested_items.name: Type
nested_items.description: The type of operation. It indicates a specific action that occured.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The current state of the operation.

nested_items.name: TargetArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the resource that the operation acted on (for example, an App Runner service).

nested_items.name: StartedAt
nested_items.description: The time when the operation started. It's in the Unix time stamp format.

nested_items.name: EndedAt
nested_items.description: The time when the operation ended. It's in the Unix time stamp format.

nested_items.name: UpdatedAt
nested_items.description: The time when the operation was last updated. It's in the Unix time stamp format.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The token that you can pass in a subsequent request to get the next result page. It's returned in a paginated request.
